Class ParameterConstants

java.lang.Object
se.oidc.nimbus.claims.ParameterConstants

    • REQUESTED_PROVIDER_PARAM_NAME

      public static final String REQUESTED_PROVIDER_PARAM_NAME
      In cases where the OpenID Provider can delegate, or proxy, the user authentication to multiple authentication services, or if the OP offers multiple authentication mechanisms, the authnProvider request parameter MAY be used to inform the OP about which of the authentication services, or mechanisms, that the Relying Party requests the user to be authenticated at/with.

      public static final String ORIGINAL_CLIENT_ID_PARAM_NAME
